name: Bukit cinta
address: GH5X+24, Sengkidu, Manggis, Karangasem Regency, Bali, Indonesia
review 1: A beautiful place and wonderful view, see the villagers' houses from a height.
review 2: Very beautiful place, see the villagers' houses from a height, there is a small shop next to it that sells hot local coffee at low prices. The majestic appearance of the majestic mountain adds to the beauty of this place.
review 3: Will get a wonderful view at the right time
